property.name: GlobalSyncId
property.description: The global unique identifier used to identify this record across applications during sync.

property.name: LineNumber
property.description: The number of the Sales Order Line. For sequencing and ordering of lines.

property.name: LineType
property.description: Enumerator indicating the type of Sales Order Line. Allowable values: Standard Line; Free text (with price); Commentary (without price, e.g. "thank you for your business!"); Component (with price but not in total); Discount/charge (included price/total)

property.name: SlxLocationId
property.description: Foreign key relationship to the SlxLocation table.

property.name: UnitOfMeasureId
property.description: Foreign key relationship to the UnitOfMeasure table

property.name: PriceDetailDescription
property.description: A short description returned by the pricing service.

property.name: PriceDetailNotes
property.description: Information from the pricing service: - Price break information that alerts the order-taker whether additional quantities purchased would result in a lower price for the customer - the discounts that the customer could qualify for if changes were made.

property.name: Tick
property.description: The vector clock incrementor used for Contract synchronization.

property.name: AppId
property.description: Foreign Key to the AppIdMapping Table. Used to track endpoint that last modified this record.
